snippet.title: Small Town Emo - Teaser
snippet.description:
Experience peak 2007 cringe! Our 1-and-a-bit-hours-long demo is out NOW! 

Jump into 2007 as emo teen Ken, hang out with your best friend Fergus and deny-deny-deny your awkward crush on him! Can you get this chemical romance sorted?

Check out the demo on itch.io now:
https://fnife-games.itch.io/emo

- - - -

CREDITS
Teaser Audio: Pickle Darling / Lukas Mayo (https://pickledarling.bandcamp.com)
Found Footage: "EMOS ARE AWESOME" Playlist, Black Veil Brides, Death Note, Invader Zim, Naruto, The Nightmare Before Christmas

- - - -

For more Fnife stuff visit us at:
https://fnifegames.com
